Definition: showing or causing joy and pleasure
Example: especially made happy; glad you are here; glad that they succeeded; gave a glad shout; a glad smile; heard the glad news; a glad occasion
Synonyms: noun, feeling, gladness, SAD, CHEERFUL, showing, or, causing, joy, and, pleasure, especially, made, happy, glad, you, are, here, that, they, succeeded, gave, a, shout, smile, heard, the, news, occasion
Category: adj.all
